alt: Photo by rhode skin on May 12, 2024. May be an image of one or more people, blonde hair and people smiling.
caption:
generations of rhode 💌

one of the biggest inspirations for rhode was hailey’s mom and nana, who taught her all about skincare at an early age. their diligent routines and love for head-to-toe hydration helped shape our approach, creating efficacious, nourishing essentials that make the most of each step in your routine.
